'''''A Teacher and a Friend: Continued''''' is an [[Adventure Mission]] on [[The Xianzhou Luofu]].

==Steps==
# Head to the Artisanship Commission and find Chengjie
# Head to Machinery District and look for standard aurumaton parts
# Hand over the parts to Chengjie
# Repair the jade abacus module of the aurumaton
# Head to Divination Commission and ask Fu Xuan for help
# Head to the Stargazer Navalia and help Xueyi capture the criminal
# Activate the Matrix of Prescience Ultima
# Return to the Matrix core and wait for Xueyi to guide the spirit
# Speak with Chengjie
# Leave the Divination Commission
# Head to Starskiff Haven and find Chengjie

