===Head to Machinery District and look for standard aurumaton parts{{subst:void|<!--202040303-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Artisanship Commission|update|You only need to change a few parts to install a starskiff's system on an aurumaton? Well, the artisan said so, so you just have to look for the parts.<br />No matter what build an aurumaton is on the Xianzhou, they use standardized parts, what an efficient design.}}
