===Hand over the parts to Chengjie{{subst:void|<!--202040304-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Artisanship Commission|update|It is as if you picked up trash by the side of the road. You pick up some standard aurumaton parts, so go ahead and hand it over to Chengjie.<br />It was supposed to be a production material requested from the Artisanship Commission... but let's not worry about that now.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{tx}}
{{Dialogue End}}

===Repair the jade abacus module of the aurumaton{{subst:void|<!--202040391-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Artisanship Commission|update|As expected, whenever there is an opportunity to make you fix jade abaci, Luofu residents will take it. Go and give them a hand.<br />You've done it a few times by now. Honestly, it's not difficult to fix, but why does nobody want to do it themselves?}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{tx}}
{{Dialogue End}}

