===Activate the Matrix of Prescience Ultima{{subst:void|<!--202040390-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Divination Commission|update|To accurately locate Master Ryan in the Hall of Karma, you need to activate the Matrix of Prescience Ultima and search for information about the deceased.<br />It sounds like the Matrix of Prescience Ultima can be used to do anything.}}
