===Return to the Matrix core and wait for Xueyi to guide the spirit{{subst:void|<!--202040313-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Divination Commission|update|The three base terminals have been activated, what was left to do is for Madam Xueyi to guide Master Ryan back to the living world. Let's go, to the Matrix core.<br />Chengjie is prepared for the aurumaton to be inhabited. It can't be the one that attacks people, can it?}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{tx}}
{{Dialogue End}}

===Speak with Chengjie{{subst:void|<!--202040314-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Divination Commission|update|Master Ryan tears apart the last of his manuscripts and wants Chengjie to pursue his own dream. What does Chengjie think about that?<br />You understand that having a pursuit is something to be encouraged, and giving up a pursuit is the same... Which decision is the right choice, that depends on you.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{tx}}
{{Dialogue End}}

===Leave the Divination Commission{{subst:void|<!--202040315-->}}===
{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Divination Commission|update|Only an awkward silence hangs in the air now. Go, leave the Divination Commission and let the Master Diviner and the judge busy themselves with their own business.<br />You understand, you should allow Chengjie some time to digest what has transpired. He'll look for you in a few days anyway.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{tx}}
{{Dialogue End}}

