{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Central Starskiff Haven|update|Chengjie seems to have recovered from his depressed episode. As he said, completing his master's final work could be a good closure, but this did not happen... Go to Starskiff Haven and talk to Chengjie again.<br />His master helped him unload the pressure he placed on himself, but it is still up to him to decide where to go next.}}
{{Dialogue Start}}
:{{tx}}
{{Dialogue End}}

